nodes.title: Auto Prompt
widgets_values: A detailed digital painting of a female knight with long, flowing red hair, wearing ornate silver and gold armor with a purple cape. She has a serious expression and is holding a sword in her right hand. The background is a dark, smoky gradient. The art style is realistic with a focus on texture and detail. The knight is positioned in the center of the image, facing the viewer.

nodes.title: Auto Prompt
widgets_values: A 3D rendering of a cute, cartoon penguin standing on a solid light blue background. The penguin has a black and white body with a yellow beak and feet, and a small tuft of black hair on its head. It has a friendly expression and is looking directly at the viewer. The lighting is soft and even, casting gentle shadows on the penguin's body. The background is simple and minimalistic, with no other objects or decorations in sight. The image is high quality and has a playful, whimsical feel.

widgets_values:
14B speedup lora doesn't support 1.3B main model

merge_loras off:
Same result for using WanVideo Set LoRAs Node or linking directly to lora slot of WanVideo Model Loder.

merge_loras on:
is only for linking directly to the lora slot of the WanVideo Model Loader and achieves a different (maybe better) result from merge_loras off.

Tune lora and lora str:
Use WanVideo Set LoRAs Node and turn off merge_loras without loading main model repeatly.

Fixed lora and test merge_loras on:
link directly to lora slot of WanVideo Model Loder and turn on merge_loras.

nodes.title: VACE Model
widgets_values:
① [Wan2.1 VACE 14B fp16 Model](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/blob/main/split_files/diffusion_models/wan2.1_vace_14B_fp16.safetensors) only  
② [Wan2.1 t2v 14B bf16 Model](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/wan2.1_t2v_14B_bf16.safetensors) + [Wan2.1 VACE 14B bf16 module model](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Wan2_1-VACE_module_14B_bf16.safetensors)  
③ [Wan2.1 t2v 14B fp8 Model](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Wan2_1-T2V-14B_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors) + [Wan2.1 VACE 14B fp8 module model](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Wan2_1-VACE_module_14B_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors)  
④ [Wan2.1 VACE 1.3B fp32 model](https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.1-VACE-1.3B/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors) only  
⑤ [Wan2.1 t2v 1.3B fp32 Model](https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors) + [Wan2.1 VACE 1.3B bf16 module model](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Wan2_1-VACE_module_1_3B_bf16.safetensors)  
⑥ [Wan2.1 VACE 1.3B fp32 preview model](https://huggingface.co/ali-vilab/VACE-Wan2.1-1.3B-Preview/blob/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors) only  
⑦ [Wan2.1 t2v 1.3B fp32 Model](https://huggingface.co/Wan-AI/Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B/resolve/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors) + [Wan2.1 VACE 1.3B bf16 module preview model](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/blob/main/Wan2_1_VACE_1_3B_preview_bf16.safetensors)

If you choose fp32/bf16/fp16/fp8 e5m2 model, then you can:
1. Link Wan Video Torch Compile Settings to the Wan Video Model Loader to speed up about 15%~25%..
